# Not committed: this sandbox can't reach services.gradle.org to generate a
# real one, and gradle/actions/setup-gradle rejects hand-made copies by
# checksum (rightly - that check exists to catch supply-chain tampering).
# Run `gradle wrapper --gradle-version 8.7` locally once to create it.
